Statistical analysis was performed using SigmaPlot version 12.5 (Systat Software, Inc., Chicago, IL, USA). Data were expressed as mean ± standard deviation (SD; 
 n = 3). One-way analysis of variance (ANOVA) followed by Dunnett’s multiple comparison test was performed to determine the significance of the differentiation and fusion indices. 
 p < 0.05 was considered significant.
